                            }
                        ],
                        "text": "The hippopotamus topiary twists and contorts its shape, shedding branches and leaves as needed to change into a topiary of a Huge or smaller animal. Until the next time it acts, the topiary has an automatic result of 42 for Deception checks and DCs to appear as a mundane topiary."
